    "Title": "~mission(ReputationRank) Hauler Needed for ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Shipment",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nJust got off a comm with a client. They got cargo (<EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> or smaller) at a few different locations ready to be taken over to a freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\n\nPICK UP LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)  \n~mission(MultiToSingleToken)  \n\nI'd recommend taking a few minutes to plan your route before taking off. Might save you a bit of fuel. And don't forget to pack a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to bring along.",
